{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3000,"text":"Allison Hunt: My three minutes hasn't started yet, has it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":5000,"text":"Chris Anderson: No, you can't start the three minutes."},{"time":7000,"text":"Reset the three minutes, that's just not fair."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"AH: Oh my God, it's harsh up here."},{"time":11000,"text":"I mean I'm nervous enough as it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"But I am not as nervous as I was five weeks ago."},{"time":18000,"text":"Five weeks ago I had total hip replacement surgery."},{"time":21000,"text":"Do you know that surgery?"},{"time":23000,"text":"Electric saw, power drill, totally disgusting"},{"time":26000,"text":"unless you're David Bolinsky, in which case it's all truth and beauty."},{"time":30000,"text":"Sure David, if it's not your hip, it's truth and beauty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"Anyway, I did have a really big epiphany around the situation,"},{"time":36000,"text":"so Chris invited me to tell you about it."},{"time":38000,"text":"But first you need to know two things about me."},{"time":40000,"text":"Just two things."},{"time":42000,"text":"I'm Canadian, and I'm the youngest of seven kids."},{"time":45000,"text":"Now, in Canada, we have that great healthcare system."},{"time":47000,"text":"That means we get our new hips for free."},{"time":49000,"text":"And being the youngest of seven,"},{"time":52000,"text":"I have never been at the front of the line for anything. OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"So my hip had been hurting me for years."},{"time":59000,"text":"I finally went to the doctor, which was free."},{"time":62000,"text":"And she referred me to an orthopedic surgeon, also free."},{"time":66000,"text":"Finally got to see him after 10 months of waiting -- almost a year."},{"time":70000,"text":"That is what free gets you."},{"time":74000,"text":"I met the surgeon, and he took some free X-rays,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and I got a good look at them. And you know,"},{"time":79000,"text":"even I could tell my hip was bad,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and I actually work in marketing."},{"time":83000,"text":"So he said, \"Allison, we've got to get you on the table."},{"time":87000,"text":"I'm going to replace your hip -- it's about an 18-month wait.\""},{"time":90000,"text":"18 more months."},{"time":92000,"text":"I'd already waited 10 months, and I had to wait 18 more months."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96000,"text":"You know, it's such a long wait that I actually"},{"time":98000,"text":"started to even think about it in terms of TEDs."},{"time":100000,"text":"I wouldn't have my new hip for this TED."},{"time":102000,"text":"I wouldn't have my new hip for TEDGlobal in Africa."},{"time":105000,"text":"I would not have my new hip for TED2008."},{"time":107000,"text":"I would still be on my bad hip. That was so disappointing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"So, I left his office and I was walking through the hospital,"},{"time":114000,"text":"and that's when I had my epiphany."},{"time":117000,"text":"This youngest of seven had to get herself to the front of the line."},{"time":121000,"text":"Oh yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"Can I tell you how un-Canadian that is?"},{"time":125000,"text":"We do not think that way."},{"time":127000,"text":"We don't talk about it. It's not even a consideration."},{"time":130000,"text":"In fact, when we're traveling abroad, it's how we identify fellow Canadians."},{"time":134000,"text":"\"After you.\" \"Oh, no, no. After you.\""},{"time":136000,"text":"Hey, are you from Canada? \"Oh, me too! Hi!\""},{"time":138000,"text":"\"Great! Excellent!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"So no, suddenly I wasn't averse to butting any geezer off the list."},{"time":145000,"text":"Some 70-year-old who wanted his new hip"},{"time":147000,"text":"so he could be back golfing, or gardening."},{"time":149000,"text":"No, no. Front of the line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151000,"text":"So by now I was walking the lobby, and of course, that hurt,"},{"time":154000,"text":"because of my hip, and I kind of needed a sign."},{"time":157000,"text":"And I saw a sign."},{"time":160000,"text":"In the window of the hospital's tiny gift shop there was a sign"},{"time":164000,"text":"that said, \"Volunteers Needed.\" Hmm."},{"time":168000,"text":"Well, they signed me up immediately."},{"time":171000,"text":"No reference checks. None of the usual background stuff, no."},{"time":174000,"text":"They were desperate for volunteers"},{"time":176000,"text":"because the average age of the volunteer at the hospital gift shop was 75."},{"time":180000,"text":"Yeah. They needed some young blood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183000,"text":"So, next thing you know, I had my bright blue volunteer vest,"},{"time":186000,"text":"I had my photo ID, and I was fully trained by my 89-year-old boss."},{"time":190000,"text":"I worked alone."},{"time":192000,"text":"Every Friday morning I was at the gift shop."},{"time":195000,"text":"While ringing in hospital staff's Tic Tacs,"},{"time":198000,"text":"I'd casually ask, \"What do you do?\""},{"time":200000,"text":"Then I'd tell them, \"Well, I'm getting my hip replaced -- in 18 months."},{"time":206000,"text":"It's gonna be so great when the pain stops. Ow!\""},{"time":211000,"text":"All the staff got to know the plucky, young volunteer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"My next surgeon's appointment was, coincidentally,"},{"time":221000,"text":"right after a shift at the gift shop."},{"time":223000,"text":"So, naturally, I had my vest and my identification."},{"time":227000,"text":"I draped them casually over the chair in the doctor's office."},{"time":229000,"text":"And you know, when he walked in,"},{"time":231000,"text":"I could just tell that he saw them."},{"time":233000,"text":"Moments later, I had a surgery date just weeks away,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and a big fat prescription for Percocet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"Now, word on the street was that it was actually"},{"time":244000,"text":"my volunteering that got me to the front of the line."},{"time":246000,"text":"And, you know, I'm not even ashamed of that."},{"time":249000,"text":"Two reasons."},{"time":250000,"text":"First of all, I am going to take such good care of this new hip."},{"time":252000,"text":"But also I intend to stick with the volunteering,"},{"time":255000,"text":"which actually leads me to the biggest epiphany of them all."},{"time":259000,"text":"Even when a Canadian cheats the system,"},{"time":262000,"text":"they do it in a way that benefits society."}]}]}